#. type: Content of: <div><div><h3>
#: _includes/support-help-band.html:3
msgid "Getting Help from the Community"
msgstr "Obter ajuda da comunidade"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><img><img><h4>
#: _includes/support-help-band.html:8
msgid "Documentation"
msgstr "Documentação"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><img><img><p>
#: _includes/support-help-band.html:9
#, fuzzy
msgid "We have a lot of documentation. Be sure to check our <a href=\"{{site.baseurl}}/get-started/\">Getting started page</a>, and all our <a href=\"{{site.baseurl}}/guides/\">guides</a>. Also check out our <a href=\"{{site.baseurl}}/faq/\">FAQ section</a> and <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLsM3ZE5tGAVbMz1LJqc8L5LpnfxPPKloO\" target=\"blank\">Quarkus Tips Playlist</a>."
msgstr "Temos muita documentação. Não deixe de consultar nossa <a href=\"{{site.baseurl}}/get-started/\">página “Introdução”</a> e todos <a href=\"{{site.baseurl}}/guides/\">os</a> nossos <a href=\"{{site.baseurl}}/guides/\">guias</a>. Confira também nossa <a href=\"{{site.baseurl}}/faq/\">seção de perguntas frequentes</a> e <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLsM3ZE5tGAVbMz1LJqc8L5LpnfxPPKloO\" target=\"blank\">a lista de reprodução “Dicas do Quarkus</a>”."

#. type: Content of: <div><div><img><img><h4>
#: _includes/support-help-band.html:14
#, fuzzy
msgid "Stack Overflow"
msgstr "Stack Overflow"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><img><img><p>
#: _includes/support-help-band.html:15
#, fuzzy
msgid "Ask your questions on <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/quarkus\" target=\"blank\">Stack Overflow</a>. After the documentation, it’s probably the best place to look for answers. We actively monitor the <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/quarkus\" target=\"blank\">Quarkus tag</a>."
msgstr "Faça suas perguntas no <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/quarkus\" target=\"blank\">Stack Overflow</a>. Depois da documentação, esse é provavelmente o melhor lugar para procurar respostas. Acompanhamos ativamente a <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/quarkus\" target=\"blank\">tag “Quarkus</a>”."

#. type: Content of: <div><div><img><img><h4>
#: _includes/support-help-band.html:20
msgid "Discussions and Collaboration"
msgstr "Discussões e Colaboração"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><img><img><p>
#: _includes/support-help-band.html:21
#, fuzzy
msgid "Check out our <a href=\"https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/discussions\" target=\"blank\">GitHub Discussions</a> collaboration area to interact with other Quarkus users and developers."
msgstr "Confira nossa área de colaboração <a href=\"https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/discussions\" target=\"blank\">“GitHub Discussions”</a> para interagir com outros usuários e desenvolvedores do Quarkus."

#. type: Content of: <div><div><img><img><h4>
#: _includes/support-help-band.html:26
#, fuzzy
msgid "Community Call"
msgstr "Chamada da Comunidade"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><img><img><p>
#: _includes/support-help-band.html:27
#, fuzzy
msgid "We host a biweekly Quarkus Community Call at 2PM (Paris time) to discuss technical topics and project updates. To attend, <a href=\"https://calendar.google.com/calendar/embed?src=935090aaae38be35eda437d018782b7827f3770f7a0344013677acd861570b20%40group.calendar.google.com&ctz=Europe%2FParis\" target=\"blank\">view the calendar</a> or <a href=\"https://calendar.google.com/calendar/ical/935090aaae38be35eda437d018782b7827f3770f7a0344013677acd861570b20%40group.calendar.google.com/public/basic.ics\">subscribe (iCal)</a> to the calendar so you don't miss one. The calls are posted to Youtube you can view the <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLsM3ZE5tGAVZ_rG48SFUFpEyTYGai0YLw\" target=\"blank\">Community Call Playlist</a> to access all of the calls."
msgstr "Realizamos uma chamada comunitária do Quarkus quinzenalmente, às 14h (horário de Paris), para discutir temas técnicos e atualizações sobre os projetos. Para participar, <a href=\"https://calendar.google.com/calendar/embed?src=935090aaae38be35eda437d018782b7827f3770f7a0344013677acd861570b20%40group.calendar.google.com&ctz=Europe%2FParis\" target=\"blank\">consulte o calendário</a> ou <a href=\"https://calendar.google.com/calendar/ical/935090aaae38be35eda437d018782b7827f3770f7a0344013677acd861570b20%40group.calendar.google.com/public/basic.ics\">inscreva-se (iCal)</a> no calendário para não perder nenhuma chamada. As chamadas são publicadas no YouTube; você pode acessar a <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLsM3ZE5tGAVZ_rG48SFUFpEyTYGai0YLw\" target=\"blank\">lista de reprodução das chamadas comunitárias</a> para assistir a todas elas."

#. type: Content of: <div><div><img><h4>
#: _includes/support-help-band.html:31
msgid "Quarkus Development"
msgstr "Desenvolvimento de Quarkus"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><img><p>
#: _includes/support-help-band.html:32
#, fuzzy
msgid "Discuss the development of Quarkus with the team in the <a href=\"mailto:quarkus-dev+subscribe@googlegroups.com\">development mailing list </a> or by <a href=\"https://quarkusio.zulipchat.com/\" target=\"blank\">Zulip Chat</a>."
msgstr "Discuta o desenvolvimento do Quarkus com a equipe na <a href=\"mailto:quarkus-dev+subscribe@googlegroups.com\">lista de discussão de desenvolvimento ou </a> pelo <a href=\"https://quarkusio.zulipchat.com/\" target=\"blank\">Zulip Chat</a>."
